This project builds on prior open-source work:

- FerSaiyan — Alternative HeyCyan App and SDK
  https://github.com/FerSaiyan/Alternative-HeyCyan-App-and-SDK
  The `glasses-capture` module (BLE photo / voice / TTS) is derived from this
  project, and the glasses Wi-Fi transfer approach started from it. Grateful
  thanks to the author.

- ebowwa — HeyCyan Smart Glasses SDK
  https://github.com/ebowwa/HeyCyanSmartGlassesSDK
  Referenced during development.

The vendor Bluetooth SDK (`glasses_sdk_*.aar`) is proprietary to the glasses
manufacturer and is NOT included in this repository. Users must supply their own
copy. See README.md.
